title: Baldwin told gun was safe before fatal shooting
content: The actor was handed the weapon by an assistant director before Halyna Hutchins was shot, a warrant says.

title: China seeks to lift homework pressure on children
content: A new law urges parents to allow children time for rest and exercise, and restrict time spent online.

title: Protesting Eswatini nurses refuse to treat police
content: The health workers say security forces injured 30 colleagues when they opened fire at a protest.
